---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Planning Disclaimer | CareCost Intelligence Cost Tools" description="Understand the planning-only limits of our senior care cost estimates, including no medical or financial advice, no guaranteed quotes, and the need to verify pricing.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="note">Updated: Feb 2026. This site provides planning information only.</p>
      <div class="tag">Last updated: Feb 2026</div>
      <div class="editorial-meta">Reviewed by CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</div>
      <div class="author-box">
        <div class="author-title">Disclaimer review</div>
        <div class="author-meta">
          <div>
            <strong>CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</strong>
            <p class="note">This disclaimer applies to our guides and estimator. For corrections, visit <a href="/contact/">contact</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chip-grid" style="margin-top: 12px;">
        <a class="chip" href="#not-advice">Not advice</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#estimates">Estimates and ranges</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#scope">Scope</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#freshness">Data freshness</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#no-endorsement">No endorsement</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#limitations">Data limitations</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#third-party">Third-party links</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#emergency">Emergency guidance</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#professional">Seek professionals</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="not-advice">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Not medical, legal, or financial advice</h2>
      <p>The estimator and guides are for planning and comparison. They do not provide medical, legal, financial, or professional advice.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="estimates">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Estimates are not quotes</h2>
      <p>All results are modeled ranges based on your inputs and general cost drivers. Actual facility pricing may differ and must be confirmed directly with providers.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Always verify pricing with local facilities.</li>
        <li>Use multiple quotes before making a decision.</li>
        <li>Consider annual price increases in long-term plans.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Inputs such as care tier, room type, and location can change totals materially, so treat estimates as directional guidance.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="scope">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Scope of guidance</h2>
      <p>This site focuses on planning for assisted living, memory care, home care, and nursing home costs. It does not provide insurance, benefits, or clinical eligibility determinations.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>We do not verify provider pricing in real time.</li>
        <li>We do not evaluate medical suitability.</li>
        <li>We do not provide legal or financial recommendations.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="freshness">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Data freshness and timing</h2>
      <p>Guidance is updated on a schedule and may not reflect rapid local pricing changes. Use the date on each page to gauge recency.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Major guides are reviewed annually.</li>
        <li>State programs and licensing details can change between reviews.</li>
        <li>Local quotes should always override generalized guidance.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="no-endorsement">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>No endorsement</h2>
      <p>References to services, facilities, or products do not constitute endorsement or recommendation. Any external links are provided for convenience.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="limitations">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Data and content limitations</h2>
      <p>Costs, program rules, and licensing guidance change over time. We summarize sources to support planning but you should confirm details with official agencies and providers.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Local pricing can vary by neighborhood and availability.</li>
        <li>Programs may have waitlists or eligibility requirements.</li>
        <li>Facilities can change pricing or service bundles without notice.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="third-party">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Third-party links</h2>
      <p>Links to government agencies, provider directories, or partner services are provided for context. We do not control external content, and link availability can change.</p>
      <p class="note">If a link is broken, let us know so we can update or replace it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="emergency">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Emergency guidance</h2>
      <p>Do not use this site for emergency decisions. If you or someone in your care needs urgent help, contact local emergency services immediately.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="professional">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Consult professionals</h2>
      <p>For care planning, medical guidance, or financial decisions, consult licensed professionals and the providers you are evaluating.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
